        {
          "scid": "an4.277-303:1.1",
          "pli": "“Rāgassa, bhikkhave, pariññāya … pe … parikkhayāya … pahānāya … khayāya … vayāya … virāgāya … nirodhāya … cāgāya … paṭinissaggāya cattāro dhammā bhāvetabbā … pe …. ",
          "en": "“For the complete understanding … finishing … giving up … ending … vanishing … fading away … cessation … giving away … letting go of greed, four things should be developed.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an4.277-303:1.2",
          "pli": "Tiṃsatimaṃ. ",
